'''iGoogle''' (formerly '''Google Personalized Homepage'''), a service of [[Google]], is a customizable [[AJAX]]-based [[startpage]] much like [[Netvibes]], [[Pageflakes]], [[My Yahoo!]] and [[Microsoft Live]]. It was originally launched in [[May 2005]]. Its features include the capability to add [[Web Feed|web feeds]] and [[Google Gadgets]] (similar to those available on [[Google Desktop]]).
